Class LockTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • LockTable

  • public class LockTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    scottfloam and pratikkarnik

    Lock Table

    The LockTable class contains a list of LockObj(s) on Variable(s) held by Transaction(s) at a given Site
